OL,7,FA robber who kicked, punched and
OL,8,Fstamped on a pensioner before stealing
OL,9,Fhis box of cornflakes and a cottage
OL,10,Fpie has been jailed for life.
OL,12,FJohn Mackey, 87, was targeted by
OL,13,Funemployed Peter Augustine, 59, after
OL,14,Fhe visited a Co-op store in Manor
OL,15,FHouse, north London, on the afternoon
OL,16,Fof May 6.
OL,18,FHe died from his injuries on Thursday,
OL,19,FMay 8.
