OL,7,FAugustine was convicted of murder and
OL,8,Frobbery by a jury at the Old Bailey
OL,9,Fearlier this month and was sentenced
OL,10,Fon Friday to life imprisonment, with a
OL,11,Fminimum term of 23 years.
OL,13,FThe court heard that passers-by saw
OL,14,FAugustine attacking Mr Mackey and
OL,15,Frifling through his jacket while he
OL,16,Flay on the ground.
