OL,7,FAugustine did not attend his
OL,8,Fbroadcasted sentencing, and Judge
OL,9,FSarah Whitehouse KC told the court: "I
OL,10,Fhave no doubt that the defendant
OL,11,Ftargeted (Mr Mackey) specifically
OL,12,Fbecause he was frail - it was a
OL,13,Fcowardly act, the defendant has shown
OL,14,Fno remorse."
OL,16,FAugustine has spent 203 days on remand
OL,17,Fand therefore has 22 years and 162
OL,18,Fdays left of his sentence to serve.
